org.bytedeco.javacpp

Class mkldnn.error

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.mkldnn.error
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    mkldnn

    @Namespace(value="mkldnn")
 @NoOffset
public static class mkldnn.error
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    Intel(R) MKL-DNN exception class. This class captures the status returned by the failed C API function, error message, and, optionally, handle of the primitive that caused the error.
